Notes: Sonic/Mid-America Intercollegiate Athletics Assn. Championships - Game 1.
Top-seeded Washburn, #9 team in NCAA-II, advances to semifinals where they'll
meet the winner of NWMSU and SBU Saturday (Mar. 8) at Noon. WU's Kristy
Chapman sets new school record for 3-pointers (112).
Game.Officials: John Murray (referee),  Amy Bonner,  Steve Krause
